{"tid":1746661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（選舉）點解香港呢個打卡風氣盛行嘅地方唔可以學下韓國咁？","createTime":"2019-11-23T00:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T00:49:39.000Z","uid":138064,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"df6ebacd4c354db3c3b3bf86862c1c6195233f76","tid":1746661,"uid":138064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T00:00:01.000Z","msg":"追開Kpop嘅唔知會唔會留意到啲韓國Idol經常會喺自己國家選舉嘅時候出post證明自己有投到票，佢地會投票嘅時候吸個印喺自己手背度，好似係佢地國家嘅潮流咁，例如係咁：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XtZsUCY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXtZsUCY.jpg&h=78666bdd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5VFGY4D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5VFGY4D.jpg&h=6882989a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z7F4cpE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz7F4cpE.jpg&h=fb0facd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係度諗點解香港唔可以用呢樣野做gimmick用吸引一眾港豬港女為咗打卡而記得去投票，可以好似#eye4hk咁create一個hashtag例如<strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#vote4hk</span></strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果唔想出樣都可以咁影<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qHt1Y7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqHt1Y7d.jpg&h=500824a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n盡量希望大家登記咗做選民都唔好嫌麻煩或者懶而唔去投票，盡返自己嘅公民責任<br />\n<br />\n祝大家1124選舉日後武運昌隆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2caf018c6b2deb9be524b727c4275e343fd01e","tid":1746661,"uid":138064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T00:00:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35a4a54b2513110a0035bc92ead585df6f300355","tid":1746661,"uid":138064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T00:01:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec1ee045900f9e1ff8a101ff0d6218b1b42e028a","tid":1746661,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T00:02:19.000Z","msg":"<